Source Notes
Graduation Rate by English Language Prof: New York City Department of Education, Graduation Results (School Years 2004-05 to 2018-19); retrieved from https://infohub.nyced.org/reports-and-policies/citywide-information-and-data/graduation-results

Name: Notes
Graduation Rate by English Language Prof:
All data represent outcomes as of June after four years of instruction. In order to comply with FERPA regulations on public reporting of education outcomes, breakdowns where the number of students in the cohort is 5 or less are suppressed and maps and tables display "no data" or "0".

Graduation rates for Former ELLs are not reported prior to 2009.
